data.description: Waterfront affordability awaits! Seize the opportunity with this cozy home in a tranquil, local-traffic-only neighborhood. Boasting TWO generous Master Bedrooms with recent updates, it offers ample square footage for versatile use. A formal living room, dining room, family room, kitchen with plenty of counter space and beautiful lanai with its own garden sanctuary round out what this home has to offer. Flower gardens and the canal leading to the Gulf of Mexico, with no bridges, are in the backyard oasis. Some features include the Tile Roof that was installed in 2013 which came with 5/8" - 5-ply plywood throughout to add extra strength, Brand New Electrical Panel installed September 2023, Hot Water Heater installed in 2021, Tile flooring throughout, and a 70 Ft Reinforced Seawall with a Cap. Enjoy fishing or relaxing after a day at work right in your backyard from the floating dock. Your Gulf Access dream home awaits - make it yours!
